#   'openapi-to-graphql'`.
#
#   `graphql/graphql-js` is **THE canonical TypeScript /
#   JavaScript GraphQL library** ŌĆö Facebook's reference JavaScript
#   implementation of the GraphQL specification, in continuous
#   active development since 2015 with 20,400+ Ōśģ on GitHub and
#   90M+ weekly npm downloads (the `graphql` package is one of
#   the top-50 most-downloaded npm packages by weekly volume).
#   It is **the JavaScript GraphQL implementation against which
#   every other JS GraphQL server tests for spec compliance**,
#   and is the underlying engine of:
#
#     ŌĆó **Apollo Server** ŌĆö the dominant production Node.js
#       GraphQL server (every Apollo Server instance imports
#       `graphql-js` for the actual GraphQL execution engine)
#     ŌĆó **GraphQL Yoga** ŌĆö The Guild's lightweight GraphQL
#       server (alternative to Apollo Server)
#     ŌĆó **Mercurius** ŌĆö Fastify-based GraphQL server
#     ŌĆó **express-graphql** ŌĆö the original express middleware
#       (this `openapi-to-graphql` CLI uses it directly)
#     ŌĆó **GraphiQL** ŌĆö the canonical browser-based GraphQL IDE
#       (every embedded GraphiQL ships graphql-js as its
#       schema-parsing + execution engine)
#     ŌĆó **Relay Compiler** ŌĆö Facebook's typed Relay framework's
#       schema validator
#     ŌĆó **Apollo Sandbox** ŌĆö Apollo Studio's embedded GraphQL
#       IDE
#     ŌĆó **Insomnia / Postman GraphQL** ŌĆö both ship graphql-js
#       for schema introspection
#     ŌĆó **Apollo Federation** ŌĆö every subgraph + supergraph
#       implementation uses graphql-js
#     ŌĆó **GitHub's GraphQL gateway** ŌĆö GitHub's entire GraphQL
#       API v4 is served by a graphql-js + custom router stack
#     ŌĆó **Shopify Admin + Storefront APIs** ŌĆö graphql-js-based
#     ŌĆó **Stripe Billing**, **Twitter GraphQL**, **Tumblr**,
#       **Pinterest**, **The New York Times Open APIs** ŌĆö all
#       graphql-js-derived servers
#     ŌĆó **Twitch's API gateway** ŌĆö Apollo Server (graphql-js
#       under the hood)
#     ŌĆó **PayPal Braintree**
#     ŌĆó **OpenAPI-to-GraphQL** (this very project)
#
#   `graphql/graphql-js` exposes:
#
#     ŌĆó Typed `buildSchema(sdl)` /  `buildASTSchema(ast)` typed
#       schema constructors that parse `.graphql` SDL files into
#       typed `GraphQLSchema` objects
